Description:
Vivendi holds a strategic global position in the content, media, and entertainment industries through the management of a unique portfolio of high-quality assets:

- Gameloft, a world-renowned global video game publisher;
- Universal Music Group, the world’s leading music company;
- Banijay, a leader in content production and an independent online sports betting company;
- TIM, Italy’s leading telecoms company with a presence in Brazil;
- MediaForEurope, a European leader in television, audiovisual production and internet;
- Telefónica, the telecommunications leader in the Spanish and Portuguese-speaking markets;
- Prisa, the media and education leader in Spain and the Spanish-speaking world.

With its diverse range of investments, Vivendi plays an active role in driving major transformations across the sectors where it operates, supporting ambitious projects aimed at sustainable growth and generating a positive impact for the future.

